      • crawl

        @RolesAllowed(value={"REGISTRY_ADMIN","REGISTRY_EDITOR"})
public void crawl(UUID datasetKey)
        This is a REST only (e.g. not part of the Java API) method that allows the registry console to trigger the crawling of the dataset. This simply emits a message to rabbitmq requesting the crawl, and applies necessary security.
